    "name": "被诅咒的小护! ReCurse",
    "steam_appid": 3273980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/6a597864f13f69cc6ae261dd007fb5a4.poster.avif?t=1771492974\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/6a597864f13f69cc6ae261dd007fb5a4.webm?t=1771492974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「…咦？这里是…」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逼近的车灯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在以为要被车撞的瞬间，时间过去了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >醒来时，Mamorukun 发现自己被传送到一个神秘的世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「嗨，大家好～！欢迎来到冥界！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据冥界的巫女「Jigokudani Fururu」的说法，她召唤了「被选中的灵魂」来拯救冥界的危机。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无视与 Mamorukun 一同被召集的少年少女们的抗议，Fururu 继续说明。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，有人试图打开通往「黑暗世界」的大门。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >因此，冥界的居民们都被诅咒了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要拯救冥界，必须净化居民，阻止黑暗世界的大门开启。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >「来吧，勇者们！为了冥界努力工作吧！」</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就这样，为了回到原本的世界，Mamorukun 等人被召唤到冥界的战斗开始了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/01e5503753fdcac1714907a3208ed681.poster.avif?t=1771492974\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/01e5503753fdcac1714907a3208ed681.webm?t=1771492974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了主射击外，还可以使用各自附身灵的力量「诅咒弹」。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单击发射「小诅咒弹」，直接命中前方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接触展开的诅咒领域，敌人和自己都会进入被诅咒状态！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >长按蓄力发射「大诅咒弹」，可以飞得更远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蓄力开始时的冲击波可以消除敌弹，并在短时间内无敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被诅咒的敌人会持续受到伤害。击倒后会大量掉落得分道具！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自己进入被诅咒状态时，力量和速度会在一定时间内提升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在诅咒状态下无法发射诅咒弹，诅咒解除后力量会下降。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握诅咒的力量，前进广大的冥界吧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/f3664ab98cc341a410c73b3efa0f3d8e.poster.avif?t=1771492974\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/f3664ab98cc341a410c73b3efa0f3d8e.webm?t=1771492974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆游戏模式</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >街机模式：游玩2008年街机版。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择关卡，注意活动时间，挑战任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事模式：2009年家用版登场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >切换角色，目标攻略全5个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冥界活剧模式：2011年家用版追加。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择3位角色，挑战指定路线。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作收录历代游戏模式、角色、服装、任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事模式新支持宽屏幕！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，还搭载了画廊模式和线上排行榜。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/ff952f792e309382c5e7772d3b42539c.poster.avif?t=1771492974\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273980/extras/ff952f792e309382c5e7772d3b42539c.webm?t=1771492974\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆音乐</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以游戏迷以外也广为人知的大热曲「YO-KAI Disco」为首，收录原版及改编版的所有BGM。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提供可依模式、关卡选择喜爱版本的BGM的自定义功能，以及可聆听所有曲目的音乐测试。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >还收录了原作作曲家 Yousuke Yasui 的新主题曲！</p>",
